@startuml SEQ-001
title SEQ-001 — Exact analysis request and persistence sequence
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial

actor User
participant "WorkspaceShell" as Workspace
participant "Context APIs" as Context
participant "/api/analyze" as Analyze
participant "OpenAI\noptional" as OpenAI
participant "/api/ai/decision-score" as Score
participant "Repository API" as Repository
database "Supabase or\nlocal fallback" as Store

User -> Workspace : choose criteria/map target and Run
Workspace -> Context : POST /api/context/market\nGET climate + validation context
Context --> Workspace : bounded context or safe fallback
Workspace -> Workspace : createMockExpressAnalysis + deterministic scores
Workspace -> Analyze : POST AnalyzeRequest
Analyze -> Analyze : isAnalyzeRequest
alt OPENAI_API_KEY present and valid response
  Analyze -> OpenAI : chat.completions JSON request
  OpenAI --> Analyze : JSON narrative
  Analyze -> Analyze : validateStructuredAnalysis
else absent, unavailable or invalid
  Analyze -> Analyze : createFallbackStructuredAnalysis
end
Analyze --> Workspace : StructuredAnalysisResult
Workspace -> Score : POST governed decision-score request
Score --> Workspace : score or null fallback
Workspace -> Workspace : merge, render and retain state
Workspace -> Repository : POST /api/analysis-runs
Repository -> Store : configured repository operation
Store --> Repository : Supabase result or local fallback result
Repository --> Workspace : mode + storage caveat
@enduml
